{"tid":2398172,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方於米埔新村檢280公斤 超過6300萬元大麻花 拘捕一名本地男子","createTime":"2021-02-07T05:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:59:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5e49153291e7e0b5e2e7c9840d27d5881a83f3","tid":2398172,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:18:02.000Z","msg":"警方前日在落馬洲米埔新村搗破一個毒品儲存倉庫，檢獲相信來自北美洲、供應本港市場的大麻花，共重280公斤，黑市價超過6300萬元，是警方歷來檢獲第二大宗的大麻花案件。行動中拘捕一名41歲報稱商人的本地男子，警方相信他是販毒集團重要人物。疑犯被暫控販運危險藥物罪，明日在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，毒品存放在涉事倉庫內的一間上鎖並長期開冷氣的房間，相信是為了去除毒品的氣味；又說雖然疫情下娛樂場所關閉，但仍有不少「暗場」有營業，因此毒品仍有市場。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，大麻花較大麻葉含毒量更高，更容易令人上癮，對身體傷害更大，近年大麻檢獲數量及吸食人數均有上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574563-20210207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574563-20210207.htm&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=739680fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574563-20210207.htm&h=cd3e3440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574563-20210207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc7fbfaa500481e7e28526531e7ab1b6b6bcca99","tid":2398172,"uid":11291,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"班狗又有免費午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ffef6685c002eafa934ab52a928a2edeb19c7a","tid":2398172,"uid":85629,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"今晚又有大餐開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3620ace906041bc3fd48f1d6850bbfdf3f82f65","tid":2398172,"uid":9502,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"dc7fbfaa500481e7e28526531e7ab1b6b6bcca99","tid":2398172,"uid":11291,"l